eli-soldier-killed-in-fighting-in-southern-gaza/00000190-5e1a-d63a-a7b2-5f1f2ee80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队表示，一名巴勒斯坦人在对杰宁的袭击中丧生。他的家人却不这么认为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-army-said-a-palestinian-was-killed-in-a-raid-his-family-believes-otherwise/00000190-5ee8-d506-ab9a-7eea278c0000</link><description>维萨姆·哈农是如军方所说，7个月前被以色列国防军杀害，还是如他父母所说，他是很久之后被拍到躺在哈达萨医院昏迷不醒的人？以色列不归还尸体的习惯让家庭在绝望与希望之间左右为难</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 13:21:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-army-said-a-palestinian-was-killed-in-a-raid-his-family-believes-otherwise/00000190-5ee8-d506-ab9a-7eea278c0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人几乎没有任何真正的共同点”：埃特加·凯雷特的采访</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israelis-hardly-have-any-true-common-denominator-an-interview-with-etgar-keret/00000190-5e82-d0b3-a7d1-7fce202d0000</link><description>对于以色列作家埃特加·凯雷特来说，即使事情分崩离析，写作仍然可以成为对话的基础。只是不要让他在反政府示威中发言</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 12:52:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israelis-hardly-have-any-true-common-denominator-an-interview-with-etgar-keret/00000190-5e82-d0b3-a7d1-7fce202d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院命令警方将缴获的模型坦克归还给抗议团体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-orders-police-to-return-model-tank-to-protest-group-after-seizing-it/00000190-5e59-d63a-a7b2-5f5f2fae0000</link><description>哈德拉治安法院法官驳回了警方的说法，即泡沫罐在凯撒利亚的反政府抗议活动中出现后，在公众中“传播了恐惧”。该模型坦克属于“Kippur 73战斗机”抗议团体</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 11:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-orders-police-to-return-model-tank-to-protest-group-after-seizing-it/00000190-5e59-