izations-in-west-bank/00000190-5ac4-d63a-a7b2-5fdf96230000</link><description>加拿大是第一个制裁约旦河西岸主要定居点组织阿马纳的政府，该组织表示其目标是在约旦河西岸安置 100 万定居者</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 18:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/canada-imposes-sanctions-on-prominent-israeli-settler-leaders-organizations-in-west-bank/00000190-5ac4-d63a-a7b2-5fdf96230000</guid></item><item><title>拜登与特朗普的辩论将是美国对以色列战争的前所未有的展示</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-27/ty-article/.highlight/biden-trump-debate-will-be-an-unprecedented-display-of-americas-wars-over-israel/00000190-590a-def3-a5b6-db2f35450000</link><description>以色列或反犹太主义很少成为美国总统辩论的核心问题。这一次，他们很可能扮演主角，尽管有些不和谐</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 17:26:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-27/ty-article/.highlight/biden-trump-debate-will-be-an-unprecedented-display-of-americas-wars-over-israel/00000190-590a-def3-a5b6-db2f35450000</guid></item></channel></rss>